After the approval required by subsection (2) of this section, a partnership may become a limited liability partnership by filing with the Secretary of State a statement of qualification. The statement shall contain:
The name of the partnership, which shall comply with KRS 14A.3-010;
The address of the partnership's chief executive office and, if different, the street address of an office in this Commonwealth, if any;
The street address of the partnership's registered office, and the name of its registered agent that comply with KRS 14A.4-010;
A statement that the partnership elects to be a limited liability partnership; and
The date any statement of partnership authority was previously filed with the Secretary of State.
